{"tid":2190730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潔篪：有個別大國唯我獨尊、強權霸淩","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T06:32:14.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64f8ce490fece3c50c0a9270c49ecd4a71925416","tid":2190730,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:55:49.000Z","msg":"中共中央政治局委員中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪批評，有個別大國唯我獨尊、強權霸淩，以冷戰思維煽動衝突對抗。<br />\n<br />\n剛結束西班牙、緬甸及希臘三國訪問行程的楊潔篪，接受新華社訪問總結此行成果，他形容這一次是深化互信之旅，拓展合作之行。<br />\n<br />\n他與三個領導人討論了加強雙邊和地區合作，就全球性挑戰問題交換意見，並達成了多項重要共識，包括推進抗疫合作及共同維護和平和發展。<br />\n<br />\n他又不點名批評，有個別大國唯我獨尊、強權霸淩，以冷戰思維煽動衝突對抗，毒化國際關係和多邊主義，將自身存在的問題歸咎於全球化，甚至諉過於人、甩鍋推責，煽動冷戰思維，製造隔閡和對立，是完全錯誤的，這種企圖也絕不會得逞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=404484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404484&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=d2311cf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404484&h=f54fabbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=404484</a>"},{"pid":"81f7acb9f0142b326cc71ac61297a27de02c0b53","tid":2190730,"uid":224533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"有自知之明係好事"},{"pid":"6e2c603f25f297966a7bea3727b9bf707fc0abf6","tid":2190730,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"仲乜咁有自知之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9399a96638506dbf8cbc77863fb37d4d458e7b6b","tid":2190730,"uid":249423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"突然自省呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b84d403e4b9915b4ff6256a5c1e839bc3dce101","tid":2190730,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20